{"tid":2080586,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"日本新推無耳帶式口罩","createTime":"2020-06-26T13:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T14:04:07.000Z","uid":198071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9565422303e9dedf4bbdba383da4b77a69dac01f","tid":2080586,"uid":198071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T13:54:55.000Z","msg":"最新咁熱相信唔少人都會想剪頭髮，但依家又成日都帶住口罩真係幾麻煩㗎。不過日本早前就推出咗兩款無耳帶式即棄口罩，真係啱晒大家喺洗頭同剪髮時用。<br />\n<br />\n口罩設計簡單，採用對肌膚甚為呵護嘅醫療用雙面膠布將口罩固定於臉上。兩款無耳帶式分喇有透明及面套兩款，兩者均用上偏薄嘅不織布所製成，透明款式可讓髮型師看到面部輪廓，而面套款式則可讓自己戴緊嘅口罩裝嵌上去，免除耳帶扣住耳仔嘅麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n兩款口罩分別有5片、10片及50片裝，售價分別為1,100日圓、1,650日圓及6,600日圓。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源：salone de mask store<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/104477835_3184075188306285_9012035313329707623_o.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_oc=AQnSX_kkgqg63tvSGudeIWsurQ-EAlZUhE_yocoeE6oOWg-kG0LFxJKQ_1t-WzUk2Kc&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=3b17b8234a9383ae798608241e7f7615&amp;oe=5F1B1182\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F104477835_3184075188306285_9012035313329707623_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_oc%3DAQnSX_kkgqg63tvSGudeIWsurQ-EAlZUhE_yocoeE6oOWg-kG0LFxJKQ_1t-WzUk2Kc%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D3b17b8234a9383ae798608241e7f7615%26oe%3D5F1B1182&h=3ae5c7bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dcb64c5708c2a289bfc783c4946ce7d12712ff6a","tid":2080586,"uid":90441,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T13:57:58.000Z","msg":"成塊m巾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5af5baf5703b4e863cfae0251be5208ab61b1ad5","tid":2080586,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T14:03:02.000Z","msg":"除兩除飲水係咪要換過塊"},{"pid":"57949f94a518393152a5f3c4ee5d849122a64775","tid":2080586,"uid":339927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T14:04:07.000Z","msg":"好似nubra"}]}